9. SCP (SSH FILE TRANSFER)
-------------------------------------------------

# Download
scp user@IP:/path/file .

# Upload
scp file user@IP:/path/

# Recursive
scp -r folder user@IP:/path/

-------------------------------------------------
10. RSYNC
-------------------------------------------------

# Copy locally
rsync -av source/ dest/

# Download
rsync -av user@IP:/dir .

# Upload
rsync -av folder user@IP:/dir

-------------------------------------------------
11. SSH
-------------------------------------------------

ssh user@IP
ssh -p 2222 user@IP
ssh -i id_rsa user@IP
ssh -X user@IP

# Execute one command
ssh user@IP "id"

